statement.p:
For the 3\times 4 matrix A and the column vector \vect{y}\in\complex{4} given below, determine if \vect{y} is in the row space of A. In other words, answer the question:  \vect{y}\in\rsp{A}?
                    A&=
                    \begin{bmatrix}
                     -2 & 6 & 7 & -1 \\
